childElements.propertySetConfig:

childElements.name: CRIR_BgInfoQ17Text

childElements.name: CRIR_BgInfoQ2Text

childElements.name: CRIR_BgInfoQ3Text

childElements.name: CRIR_BgInfoQ4Text
childElements.propertySetConfig:
{ "controlWidth" : 10, "text" : "

4) SINCE YOUR LAST APPLICATION, have you been convicted by final judgment of a felony? ", "label" : "TextBlock3", "HTMLTemplateId" : "", "sanitize" : false, "textKey" : "", "dataJSON" : false }
